  "Description": "The PCM Series comprises ultraminiature, low-profile, surface-mount slide switches available in SPDT (Single Pole Double Throw) and SP3T (Single Pole Triple Throw) configurations. They function as manual electromechanical selectors, connecting a common terminal to one of several output terminals depending on the actuator's position. Designed for automated assembly, they are RoHS compliant and packaged on tape and reel for high-volume applications in computer peripherals, telecommunications, and test equipment.",
